{"type": "article", "id": 35607, "title": "这个酒瓶，同时也是月相日历｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-14T23:08:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35835, "name": "PRAXIS DESIGN"}, {"id": 35836, "name": "Privacy Pop"}, {"id": 35837, "name": "Javier Garduño Design Studio"}, {"id": 25981, "name": "Quentin de Coster"}, {"id": 34828, "name": "Reinier de Jong"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 109, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161215001348D617CgaQRkjhZrLi.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>MEMO-O by Quentin de Coster</h3><p>笔和即时贴都是常用的办公用品，然而它们会因为种种原因分开放置。比利时设计师 <a href=\"https://www.quentindecoster.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Quentin de Coster</a> 想到了一个简单的解决方式，他将笔筒的功能和即时贴融合，为香港设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.praxis-design.com.hk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">PRAXIS DESIGN</a> 设计了一款圆柱形的即时贴 MEMO-O。这款即时贴的中央有一个圆孔，免去了要写字时额外找笔的烦恼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612150016134RoWDxbdFrGAYa9g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001613dEiM1n7jI4NTuxlL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001613LrOjZ0y3If4VXGdT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612150016143uQGzqiR7rfsNVxB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>REK coffee table by Reinier de Jong</h3><p>为了迎合人们在不同场合下对家具的要求，荷兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.reinierdejong.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reinier de Jong</a> 带来了这款像是积木玩具一样可以灵活变化的咖啡桌 REK。这张桌子由三部分组成，中间两层可以独立地在两个方向上移动，内置的固定系统又保证它们不至于滑出。它的表面采用实木和白色的防火板（HPL）制成，订制时还可以在三种木材中进行挑选。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001633WonbIlPpF7Kij0S1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001633GDXZ5zTSUKvxPe4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001634z1ktf2pmj0ghRlHa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001635IB1VCgGKtQ68oFU9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Bed Tent by Privacy Pop</h3><p>如果你既重视睡眠质量和个人隐私，不妨来看看美国设计品牌 <a href=\"https://www.privacypop.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Privacy Pop</a> 推出的这款 The Bed Tent。从直白的产品名就能看出它其实是一个配合已有床铺使用的帐篷，四周既有门也有纱窗，方便用户调整内部的光线和空气。帐篷采用了扁平化的设计，安装的过程并不繁琐，平时还可以收纳成一个圆形小袋，不会占用过多空间。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.privacypop.com/shop/tent/privacy-pop-bed-tent/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，根据床铺的尺寸，售价从 119.99 到 199.99 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001653tSFdCGwq1loWI7MX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001653V3JNzKMol5APbSwZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.787654\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001653Ii2j9YORgJf7qL5W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.848148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001653wVZipKbFou4O6cGe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.888889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001653pKItnJG7udFhLi1H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.801235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tectonic clock by Andreas Vang</h3><p>以日晷为灵感，通过光影呈现时间变化的时钟也可以玩出新花样，在荷兰工作的丹麦设计师 <a href=\"http://www.andreasvang.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Andreas Vang</a> 最近就带来了一款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/45965891/TECTONIC-CLOCK\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tectonic clock</a> 的概念设计。它的最外层被分成了 60 个板块，会根据时间变化凸起并在表面形成阴影。其中单独凸起的那一块表示分针，三块同时凸起时中间那块则代表时针。美中不足的是，它并没有时间符号，只通过一个小缺口来表示 12 点的位置，要确认时间颇为困难。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001725e04xNUvlW2ftpKbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001726wt4sPnXMv0QA3eN9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001726nZQXwebBtPYFuVOm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.798095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001725Rn43EjPkhY0MH2Xw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Audi iron by Jaehyuk Lim</h3><p class=\"\">面对千篇一律的熨斗造型，韩国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/junglehouse\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jaehyuk Lim</a>&nbsp;决定打造一款让人们在使用后乐意放在外面的产品，并最终选择了奥迪作为灵感来源。这个名为 Audi iron 的概念产品通过内置电池运作，省去了整理电线的麻烦。它的底部有一条橙色的 LED 指示灯，同时也直观地反映出温度的高低。当这样的熨斗在衣服上游走时，或许真的会有一种驾驭迷你型奥迪汽车的错觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001438XhKURZ5dkIJxqm96.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001439DkAUzyiCmshr9PKX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001439AMUrHbgmEDiLd52f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001439YaEj5chKbZPtuTxM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704762\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001440TmRaZtWncYQVSB9U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001439fqBnYr7CNJ49IceS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lunar Calendar Wine by Javier Garduño Design Studio</h3><p>月相日历并不是什么新奇的设计，然而它和葡萄酒包装的组合就很少见了。西班牙设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.javiergarduno.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Javier Garduño</a> 最近为葡萄酒品牌 <a href=\"http://www.bigardo.es/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kiko Calvo</a> 设计了一款独特的包装：1.5 升的瓶身上有一张采用丝网印刷的 2017 年月相日历，瓶颈处是一条印有月面图案的纸带，末端还配有细棍。月、日都可以通过调整两者的位置达成，无论是提醒自己什么时候开了这瓶酒还是喝完后作为日历使用都很方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001420JGD3ygmfohT24QZs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001420B65fvnq97aNFHAwu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001420vWQj54yTq1dCPGkB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215001419hvAxkGZcQM154bBO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}